						<a class="external" target="_blank" rel="noopener follow" href="https://www.jj5.net/wiki/Rigol_MSO5074" title="Click here for notes about this equipment which I keep on my personal wiki.">my notes</a>.</p>
					<p>If you would like to see all of my equipment check out the 
